<p>I did a quick read of the Value vs Risk document provided. My first impression is that some responses are a bit &quot;vague&quot; but the most important one is the answer to question 9 <em>&quot;To what extent have CA personnel reviewed the CA incidents that have been reported in Bugzilla over the past several years? How have systems been designed to avoid similar mistakes&quot;</em>.</p>
